last_episode_to_air.overview: Henry and the Party Down crew scheme to keep their latest party going all night.

name: Party Down
overview: A group of struggling actors and dysfunctional dreamers wait for their big break while they are stuck serving hors d'oeurves for a Hollywood catering company 'Party Down.'

seasons.name: Season 3
seasons.overview: 10 years later, most of the Party Down catering team have moved on, including actor/bartender Henry Pollard. After a surprise reunion, the gang find themselves once again stoically enduring the procession of random parties and oddball guests all over Los Angeles.

episodes.name: Willow Canyon Homeowners Annual Party
episodes.overview: Failed actor Henry Pollard returns to work at Party Down catering. He meets his fellow employees, led by his old coworker Ron, a clean-living team leader with big dreams.

episodes.name: California College Conservative Union Caucus
episodes.overview: At a college conservatives event, students aim to give the Party Down team advice on success. As the event goes on, it turns out the students may not be so bright.

episodes.name: Pepper McMasters Singles Seminar
episodes.overview: The Party Down team caters a senior singles mixer hosted by Pepper McMasters. Constance has an awkward encounter with an old flame and Casey seeks relationship advice.

episodes.name: Investors Dinner
episodes.overview: A land tycoon expects flawless service from the Party Down crew, but Ron's dreams of success threaten to ruin everything. Kyle makes a friend whose lifestyle he hopes to emulate.

episodes.name: Sin Say Shun Awards After Party
episodes.overview: The Party Down team caters a porn awards afterparty. Kyle tries to teach Roman to "play it cool" with the porn stars. A mysterious businessman makes Ron a surprising business offer.

episodes.name: Taylor Stiltskin Sweet Sixteen Party
episodes.overview: Taylor Stiltskin's film producer father is throwing her the perfect sweet 16--only nobody showed up! Henry runs into an old friend. Ron gets business advice from a rap duo.

episodes.name: Brandix Corporate Retreat
episodes.overview: When the Party Down team caters the Brandix corporate retreat, Casey strikes up a friendship with the sports star guest speaker, making both Henry and Roman jealous.

episodes.name: Celebrate Ricky Sargulesh
episodes.overview: The Party Down team's actors are recognized at a party and treated as stars. But when Roman and Ron discover the host is a mobster, they suspect his screenplay might be a confession.

episodes.name: James Rolf High School Twentieth Reunion
episodes.overview: Ron decides to cater his own reunion, and begins to slip back into his old drunken habits. Henry considers moving home, causing Casey to consider their "casual" relationship.

episodes.name: Stennheiser-Pong Wedding Reception
episodes.overview: In the season finale, the team is excited to cater a lavish gay wedding, but must take a backseat to the chiseled men of the Adonis catering company. While Ron falls apart, Henry is forced to take charge.

episodes.name: Jackal Onassis Backstage Party
episodes.overview: As the struggling new Party Down team leader, Henry is forced to juggle an incognito rock star, the return of of Ron Donald and Casey, the girl who broke his heart.

episodes.name: Precious Lights Pre-School Auction
episodes.overview: Having trouble letting go of his leadership position, Ron and Henry clash at a fundraiser where parents will do anything to get their kids into an exclusive elementary school.

episodes.name: Nick DiCintio's Orgy Night
episodes.overview: Catering an orgy proves to be the wrong place for Ron to deal with his recent breakup. Roman seizes the opportunity to help the host create the ideal orgy atmosphere.

episodes.name: James Ellison Funeral
episodes.overview: The funeral of a patriarch goes awry when the deceased's mistress arrives to pay her last repects. Kyle is mesmerized by the possibility of learning the blues from a real bluesman.

episodes.name: Steve Guttenberg's Birthday
episodes.overview: At his own birthday, Steve Guttenberg volunteers to turn his party into a writing workshop when he overhears Roman and writing partner Kent discussing their script.

episodes.name: Not On Your Wife Opening Night
episodes.overview: At a community theater, the onstage farce trickles into real life as Kyle promises to help his old mentor by romancing a wealthy female patron with the funds to save the theater.

episodes.name: Party Down Company Picnic
episodes.overview: Competition is the word of the day as Ron competes for a job at the head office, Casey for best all around at the events and Roman and Kyle compete with Val Halla catering.

episodes.name: Joel Munt's Big Deal Party
episodes.overview: Roman is less than thrilled when he discovers the party is being thrown by his 'sell-out' writing partner who hired him to rub his face in the sale of his new spec script.

episodes.name: Cole Landry's Draft Day Party
episodes.overview: When top college QB Cole Landry unexpectedly slips in the draft, rumors begin circulating that tangle Casey and Henry in the secret lives of college athletes.

episodes.name: Constance Carmell Wedding
episodes.overview: Constance is getting married and she's hired her Party Down friends to make sure they attend. Ron, guided by Constance's wisdom to 'follow your heart', makes a desperate bid for love.

episodes.name: Kyle Bradway Is Nitromancer
episodes.overview: Ten years later, Kyle Bradway has just landed his star-making superhero role. He hires Party Down to cater his celebration party, leading to welcome reunions and some unexpected surprises.

episodes.name: Jack Botty's Delayed Post-Pandemic Surprise Party
episodes.overview: Party Down works a surprise party for movie star Jack Botty thrown by his studio exec girlfriend Evie, which turns weird when the team sees something they shouldnt have.

episodes.name: First Annual PI2A Symposium
episodes.overview: Ron, desperate to keep Party Down afloat, books an event for an extremely problematic group leading to complications for everyone.

episodes.name: KSGY-95 Prizewinner's Luau
episodes.overview: Hired to work a laid-back radio promotion luau in groovy Malibu, the gang decides to take mushrooms together and things get weird.

episodes.name: Once Upon a Time "Proms Away" Prom-otional Event
episodes.overview: Lydia, worried that daughter Escapade missed her childhood, plans a prom promotional event for her new movie. Meanwhile, Ron schemes to impress a studio PR bigwig who could make or break Party Down.

episodes.name: Sepulveda Basin High School Spring Play Opening Night
episodes.overview: Henry and the Party Down crew scheme to keep their latest party going all night.
